Hey Marcus! Good to see you! 👋

Just wrapped up the morning queue review - here's where we stand:

**Current Support Status:**
• 40 tickets in queue, all being processed
• Maintaining our 3.2-hour average response time
• CSAT holding steady at 4.4/5 - customers are happy with our service

**What I'm Seeing Today:**
• **Shipping inquiries** leading the pack (14 tickets) - mostly WISMO questions and delivery timing
• **Account management** requests up (10 tickets) - lots of subscription upgrades, which is actually great news
• **Product feedback** flowing in (8 tickets) - customers sharing recipe ideas and reviews

The team's hitting our targets, and nothing's escalated to urgent status. Quality issues are minimal (just 4 tickets), so our product standards are holding strong.

Anything specific you want me to dig into, or shall I keep you posted on any patterns that emerge throughout the day?
